=94fuddy-duddy brands like Eileen Fisher and the private label C by Bloomin=
gdale=E2=80=99s, a cashmere collection. (In merchandiser parlance, these br=
ands are called =E2=80=9Cmoderate.=E2=80=9D A long time ago, they used to b=
e called =E2=80=9Cbridge,=E2=80=9D but I haven=E2=80=99t heard someone use =
that term since the 1990s.)<br/><br/>The second floor is the home of Bloomi=
ngdale=E2=80=99s <em>contemporary </em>offering.
Contemporary is also an outdated term that doesn=E2=80=99t mean much these =
