 than =E2=80=9Cmoderate=E2=80=9D lines, but more gently priced than designe=
r goods. Given that Ralph Lauren has become a cool brand with Gen Z=E2=80=
=94thanks in part to the latter=E2=80=99s ability to buy it for cheap and s=
