b952047e6c06ec6c0bccc5f339c2edcd45d51986a7778cc0b539" style=3D"text-decorat=
ion:underline;color:#d40000;">Adidas Samba</a>, which has ascended to Line =
Sheet cinematic universe status of late. This retro European football
sneaker became so popular that it sparked a broader obsession with low-prof=
ile, vintage-inspired kicks=E2=80=94most notably, the German Army Trainer (=
GAT). In fact, the GAT has become <em>the</em> insider=E2=80=99s alternativ=
e to the ubiquitous Samba=E2=80=94the embodiment of a retro wave of <em>qui=
